So, we're going to pray tonight over this nation and this storm, and we're going to keep calling it to weaken and move faster.

01:27:02.815 --> 01:27:12.194
I told the Lord—the Lord said, "Brandon," when I was praying over it—I said, "What about slowing it down and bringing in the colder air quicker?

01:27:14.766 --> 01:27:16.250
" That was my problem-solving with the things I've overcome.

01:27:22.799 --> 01:27:23.079
And I was talking to God, "Daddy, wouldn't it be better to go faster?

01:27:23.079 --> 01:27:24.200
Let's move it.

01:27:24.200 --> 01:27:26.400
Let's get it out of here quick.

01:27:26.400 --> 01:27:31.406
Let's get that low pressure out of here as fast as possible.

01:27:31.406 --> 01:27:43.700
" I'm thinking, "Well, if we could just get the cold air down and move it up north, the snow could happen up there.

01:27:43.700 --> 01:27:51.177
" Chicago is used to snow; we're not used to ice down here in Oklahoma and Texas.

01:27:51.177 --> 01:27:56.130
But in my mind, I'm thinking you've got to think smarter.

01:27:56.130 --> 01:27:58.149
That's what I'm telling you.

01:27:58.149 --> 01:28:00.319
It's just Jesus.

01:28:00.319 --> 01:28:05.223
All glory to God when it comes to Brandon.

01:28:05.223 --> 01:28:12.739
I feel the anointing of the Holy Ghost now; I'm so thankful that He would come.

01:28:31.340 --> 01:28:31.560
I pray for this great nation that it remains great.

01:28:31.560 --> 01:28:36.840
He said, "I will not allow your nation to become a goat nation.

01:28:51.600 --> 01:28:51.840
I will keep you a sheep nation.

01:28:51.840 --> 01:28:58.020
" When I talked about the wound and the things that I saw, I didn't know what it was.

01:28:58.020 --> 01:29:00.274
But now you can see what it was.

01:29:02.126 --> 01:29:11.553
It would be a wound that would not be fatal, but it would shake the church through the valley of decision.

01:29:11.553 --> 01:29:13.599
It's His choice.

01:29:13.599 --> 01:29:19.1000
Do you go this way, or are you going to go that way?

01:29:19.1000 --> 01:29:22.399
Go the right path.

01:29:22.399 --> 01:29:27.417
From Jesus, we pray for your safety.

01:29:27.417 --> 01:29:31.040
This is what the Lord said, not Brandon.

01:29:31.040 --> 01:29:34.099
This is what I saw from the Heavenly Father.

01:29:50.516 --> 01:29:50.907
And He said, "Pray for him.

01:29:50.907 --> 01:29:54.000
Pray for the counsel that is around him.

01:29:56.857 --> 01:29:59.250
For I have a plan for his life, but he's in the valley of decision.

01:29:59.250 --> 01:30:00.840
" What will you choose today?

01:30:02.560 --> 01:30:02.780
To follow Jesus.

01:30:02.780 --> 01:30:10.800
He spared him once; He spared him twice on the golf course, and even more times that we probably don't even know about.

01:30:10.800 --> 01:30:25.463
A thousand shall fall at your side and ten thousand at your right hand, but nothing shall come nigh you.

01:30:25.463 --> 01:30:33.840
Humble yourself underneath the mighty hand of God, and in due time He will exalt you.

01:30:33.840 --> 01:30:39.223
You're in the time of the valley of decision coming into November.

01:30:52.808 --> 01:30:52.977
And that's what the Lord said.

01:30:52.977 --> 01:31:00.440
After all that, I found out that his wife's pregnant with child; she's due in July from what I understand.

01:31:00.440 --> 01:31:04.239
When I heard that, I about fell over.

01:31:04.239 --> 01:31:06.880
My son said, "Daddy, JD Vance's wife's pregnant.

01:31:06.880 --> 01:31:10.090
" So, will you help me, church?

01:31:10.090 --> 01:31:11.170
Can we pray?

01:31:11.170 --> 01:31:13.390
Will you take it seriously?

01:31:13.390 --> 01:31:17.312
It's not here for your entertainment.

01:31:17.312 --> 01:31:26.969
I've been assigned by the Lord Jesus to tell you of what's to come and how we can change it through prayer.

01:31:26.969 --> 01:31:28.196
So, we're going to pray now.

01:31:28.196 --> 01:31:36.359
We're going to take communion and we're going to pray for our president and that he'll make godly decisions concerning Greenland.

01:31:36.359 --> 01:31:37.360
Maybe there's another way.

01:31:37.560 --> 01:31:44.868
You know, some say he won't take it by military force.

01:31:44.868 --> 01:31:49.199
