01:31:50.914 --> 01:32:03.333
All I know is the Lord said it's concerning Greenland and the decisions concerning Europe and Iran in the days ahead, and how he handles Israel and Gaza and all the things ahead of it.

01:32:03.333 --> 01:32:06.560
I've warned about splitting Jerusalem, a two-state solution.

01:32:06.560 --> 01:32:12.864
I said if that happens, I saw America be split right down the middle.

01:32:12.864 --> 01:32:17.476
I don't believe he's for a two-state solution.

01:32:17.476 --> 01:32:22.373
All I know is just to pray because that's as far as the word went.

01:32:22.373 --> 01:32:26.120
So what he's supposed to do, I have no idea.

01:32:26.120 --> 01:32:35.992
He didn't say, "Brandon, I want you to be on his counseling board and tell him what to do.

01:32:35.992 --> 01:32:37.384
" He said, "Pray for him.

01:32:37.384 --> 01:32:41.690
" He didn't say, "Well, you have it all figured out, Brandon.

01:32:55.573 --> 01:33:00.031
I want to send you there and you can go and talk to him and tell him what's going to be—how the cow ate the cabbage.

01:33:00.031 --> 01:33:02.583
" He said, "I want you to intercede on your platform.

01:33:10.940 --> 01:33:11.130
" So everybody said, "What's the choice?

01:33:11.130 --> 01:33:12.329
How do we stop this?

01:33:12.329 --> 01:33:13.822
" I don't have a clue.

01:33:15.177 --> 01:33:17.280
All I know is the Lord said to pray.

01:33:30.053 --> 01:33:30.600
So that's what I have.

01:33:32.799 --> 01:33:33.079
I did it.

01:33:33.079 --> 01:33:34.200
I delivered it.

01:33:37.140 --> 01:33:37.560
That was so hard.

01:33:41.810 --> 01:33:44.899
When you get something off your back you've been carrying for a while, it feels better.

01:33:45.899 --> 01:33:56.740
The Lord said, "I told you I was going to have you say the hard things, and that wasn't even hard compared to what you'll say in the future.

01:33:57.560 --> 01:34:00.888
" And I said, "Oh, God," because that was hard.

01:34:00.888 --> 01:34:02.799
So we pray over it.

01:34:12.389 --> 01:34:12.651
All right.

01:34:12.651 --> 01:34:16.400
So, Father, we lift up the body.

01:34:16.400 --> 01:34:27.324
We thank you, Lord, for the body that was broken for us.

01:34:41.101 --> 01:34:41.483
We thank you, Lord, that you're our healer.

01:34:58.845 --> 01:34:59.199
You are our deliverer.

01:34:59.199 --> 01:35:06.700
And we thank you, Lord, that by your stripes, we're healed.

01:35:06.700 --> 01:35:10.444
Lord, we take this and we're so grateful for all that you've done.

01:35:10.444 --> 01:35:11.965
We thank you, Father.

01:35:11.965 --> 01:35:27.189
We take this body in the name of Jesus and we give you all the glory, honor, and praise for it in Jesus' name.

01:35:27.199 --> 01:35:28.439
Amen.

01:35:28.439 --> 01:35:29.679
Amen.

01:35:29.679 --> 01:35:34.249
Now Lord, if you want to show us anything else, we yield ourselves to you.

01:35:43.679 --> 01:35:49.280
I yield to the anointing of the prophetic and I thank you, Father, that we fly like the eagles and we see that which is to come.

01:36:12.658 --> 01:36:12.915
I plead the blood of Jesus over me, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:36:16.1000 --> 01:36:19.199
I apply the blood of Jesus over us.

01:36:19.199 --> 01:36:22.400
We thank you, Lord.

01:36:22.400 --> 01:36:28.520
We make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

01:36:46.910 --> 01:36:52.053
We plead the blood in the name of Jesus.

01:36:52.053 --> 01:36:57.400
We thank you, Lord, that your hand is on us.

01:37:02.342 --> 01:37:03.668
And we give you glory, honor, and praise in the name of Jesus.

01:37:03.668 --> 01:37:04.857
We thank you.

01:37:04.857 --> 01:37:14.747
We confess our sins before you, Father, and you are faithful and just to forgive us of our sins and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

01:37:14.747 --> 01:37:17.897
Lord, we're just here for you.

01:37:23.160 --> 01:37:23.440
And we yield ourselves to you tonight, Father.

01:37:23.440 --> 01:37:30.453
I apply the blood over this room.

01:37:30.453 --> 01:37:48.045
I apply the blood over my children, over us, our finances, everything, Father.

01:37:48.045 --> 01:37:52.351
I cover us in the blood, Father.

01:37:52.351 --> 01:37:54.091
I thank you, Lord.

01:37:54.091 --> 01:37:59.733
No weapon formed against us will prosper in the mighty name of Jesus.

01:37:59.733 --> 01:38:00.907
Amen and amen.

01:38:12.368 --> 01:38:12.896
Take the blood.

01:38:12.896 --> 01:38:17.410
He said do this often in remembrance of me and what he did for us.

01:38:17.410 --> 01:38:21.417
Jesus paid the price and he made us free.

01:38:21.417 --> 01:38:22.651
Isn't he wonderful?

01:38:22.651 --> 01:38:24.120
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

01:38:26.514 --> 01:38:29.280
We give all of the glory to Jesus and tell of his wonderful love.

01:38:29.280 --> 01:38:30.436
So, let's pray now.

01:38:30.436 --> 01:38:35.340
Who wants to go tubing for a little bit?

01:38:35.340 --> 01:38:36.489
