01:38:41.131 --> 01:38:42.900
Hour and 20 minutes.

01:38:42.900 --> 01:38:43.400
Almost.

01:38:43.400 --> 01:38:44.773
Well, that was great.

01:38:44.773 --> 01:38:47.215
It is what it is.

01:38:47.215 --> 01:38:53.360
If you want to be here, be here.

01:38:53.360 --> 01:38:54.846
If you don't, don't.

01:38:54.846 --> 01:39:00.400
So, Father, we just lift up this time before you and we just thank you.

01:39:00.400 --> 01:39:03.904
