01:39:12.780 --> 01:39:16.800
Father, we cover President Trump in the name of Jesus and we lift up his family, his wife, his sons, his daughters, his grandchildren.

01:39:34.380 --> 01:39:34.680
We thank you, Lord, that there's a hedge around and about them.

01:39:34.680 --> 01:39:49.737
I thank you, Father, as the church that prays, believers, that we take authority over the evil counsel in the name of Jesus that has surrounded him.

01:39:51.280 --> 01:39:54.628
We say, "Satan, thus far and no further.

01:39:54.628 --> 01:39:59.547
" We plead the blood of Jesus over our nation, over our president, over his cabinet.

01:39:59.547 --> 01:40:04.914
We thank you, Lord, that you expose and remove the rats.

01:40:04.914 --> 01:40:10.400
We command the rats to go, Father—the people that are there on ill assignment from the enemy.

01:40:15.380 --> 01:40:20.944
Father, I thank you that you would expose them through a text or through what they say, that they'll be caught in what they do.

01:40:27.508 --> 01:40:32.360
Father, for the people that are supposed to be around him, let there be a peace that flows through him.

