He would know, "You know what?

01:40:56.239 --> 01:40:56.737
I know this is just right.

01:41:00.221 --> 01:41:14.569
" And where the enemy is trying to do evil counsel and ungodly thoughts, we thank you that there's confusion in every evil work, so much so that they'll not be able to get it out right because there's no flow over it.

01:41:14.569 --> 01:41:22.400
It'll just be like, "I don't even know what I'm saying.

01:41:22.400 --> 01:41:33.737
" There'll be a confusion, Father, over the evil and a flow with the good.

01:41:33.737 --> 01:41:37.400
Godly counsel will stand and flow.

01:41:37.400 --> 01:41:39.657
Evil counsel will fall.

01:41:39.657 --> 01:41:59.040
And we thank you, Lord, that they'll not even be able to get it done because the hand of the Lord is upon them.

01:42:00.480 --> 01:42:06.329
We thank you, Lord, that the hand of the Lord is moving in our behalf.

01:42:06.329 --> 01:42:11.177
Father, you're our Father and you told us to pray.

01:42:11.177 --> 01:42:14.948
So, we humble ourselves before you, Father.

01:42:17.600 --> 01:42:26.560
We know we can't do this without you.

01:42:26.560 --> 01:42:36.066
But God, you told us to take our authority.

01:42:36.639 --> 01:42:38.788
You said that you've given us power and authority.

01:42:41.779 --> 01:42:48.610
I believe tonight, Lord, we take our rightful place of authority over this nation, over our president.

